    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏交流群：614389592</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏使用了简单的翻牌机制，模拟在夜晚的街道探索的过程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336590/extras/e3272e36ad8e6b3ce17117e4aa27d412.avif?t=1771997802\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >街道中每个地点存有不同数量的卡牌，玩家通过以合理的顺序点击卡牌来通过地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336590/extras/41dd4a51714289a49b2ed5fcd11dae19.avif?t=1771997802\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌有单纯的伤害牌(精神上的伤害)，恢复用的道具牌，免于伤害的装备牌，和各种各样的特效牌等等，以合理的顺序点击卡牌是过关的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336590/extras/416c72de378dd8ab1f49206e2424f29f.avif?t=1771997802\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，你也可以通过技能进行洗牌。除了洗牌，你还会在游戏过程中获得更多的技能，可以形成各种各样强力的组合，来帮助你度过各种考验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336590/extras/2c0761346a7a0f47efa52ec185955184.avif?t=1771997802\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >技能来源于不同的角色，你会在游戏中的各种地点碰到他们，而和角色们的相遇会推动故事的进展，直到这一夜的结束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336590/extras/b5cf6880087b6f845c223972da72abf8.avif?t=1771997802\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者永远不会结束？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336590/extras/ee911ba38cb6dbf9771069794a9d42ed.poster.avif?t=1771997802\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336590/extras/ee911ba38cb6dbf9771069794a9d42ed.webm?t=1771997802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336590/extras/ee911ba38cb6dbf9771069794a9d42ed.mp4?t=1771997802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏在研发过程中结合了一定的AI技术支持，如您对此有特殊偏好或顾虑，还请酌情选择是否体验。感谢您的理解与支持。</p></li></ul>",
